generateProducts

protected static void generateProducts(java.util.Vector<DisplayMetricResult> res,
                                       boolean dG,
                                       boolean wG,
                                       boolean dN,
                                       boolean wN,
                                       WriteOption write,
                                       boolean guiCall)
                                throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
Generates and displays the specified products.

Parameters:
res - the results from which to generate products
dG - is true to display graphics
wG - is true to write graphics
dN - is true to display numerics
wN - is true to write numerics
write - the additional charting options for the specified type
guiCall - is true if calling this method from the GUI, false otherwise
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
